    metaDescription: 'Discover how the Current Account Switch Service (CASS) simplifies changing your UK business bank account. Learn about eligibility, benefits, and the process.',
    h1: 'What Is the Current Account Switch Service (CASS) for Businesses?',
    intro: `Are you considering moving your business finances to a new provider but worried about the hassle? The Current Account Switch Service (CASS) is designed to make changing your business bank account in the UK simple, reliable, and stress-free. In this comprehensive guide, we will explore exactly what CASS is, how it works for businesses, and the key benefits of using this guaranteed service.`,
